text: Viola Lynn Collins (born May 16, 1977) is an American actress. She has made television appearances in True Blood (2008) and Manhunt: Unabomber (2017). She also starred in the movies X-Men Origins: Wolverine (2009) and John Carter (2012). ==References== Category:1977 births Category:Living people Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:American stage actors Category:American voice actors Category:Actors from Houston
